Exercise 4 — Tasks
List all directors of Pixar movies (alphabetically), without duplicates
QUERY- SELECT DISTINCT DIRECTOR FROM MOVIES ORDER BY DIRECTOR ASC;

List the last four Pixar movies released (ordered from most recent to least)
QUERY- SELECT *FROM MOVIES ORDER BY YEAR DESC LIMIT=4;

List the first five Pixar movies sorted alphabetically
QUERY- SELECT * FROM MOVIES ORDER BY TITLE ASC LIMIT 5;

List the next five Pixar movies sorted alphabetically
QUERY - SELECT * FROM MOVIES ORDER BY TITLE ASC LIMIT 5 OFFSET 5;
